h \to 0
 \lim_{h \to 0}\frac{\sin(x + h) - \sin(x)}{h} 
 \frac{\sin(x + h) - \sin(x)}{h} = \frac{\sin(x)\cos(h) + \sin(h)\cos(x) - \sin(x)}{h}\\\\ = \frac{\cos(h) - 1}{h}\sin(x) + \frac{ \sin(h)}{h}\cos(x) 
